1289:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Structure.c **** *  This function reports if the specified sensor in the widget has detected a
1290:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Structure.c **** *  touch or not by extracting information from the wdgtStatus registers
1291:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Structure.c **** *  (CapSense_WDGT_STATUS<X>_VALUE). This function does not process the
1292:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Structure.c **** *  widget or sensor but extracts processed results from the \ref group_structures.
1293:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Structure.c **** *
1294:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Structure.c **** *  For proximity sensors, this function returns the proximity detection status. To
1295:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Structure.c **** *  get the finger touch status of proximity sensors, use the
ARM GAS  C:\Users\ash750\AppData\Local\Temp\ccIeODta.s 			page 38


